      <body><div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><salute><pb facs="HS_AM23333Ba"/>Lieber Freund,</salute></opener><p>ich beglückwünſche dich von Herzen zu deinem großen <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="KL021-1"/>Erfolg<note type="commentary" xml:id="KL021-1h">Uraufführung von <rs ref="#30127" type="work">Der Star</rs> am <date>12. 11. 1898</date> im <rs ref="#35053" type="org">Lessingtheater</rs> in <rs ref="#168" type="place">Berlin</rs>.</note> in <rs ref="#168" type="place">Berlin</rs>, <unclear>und</unclear> grüße dich vielmals </p><closer>dein <signed>Arthur Schnitzler</signed></closer><postscript><p><rs ref="#50" type="place">Wien</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date when="1898-11-13">13. 11. 98.</date></p></postscript></div></body>
